<h2 id="api">API</h2>

<h3 id="parameters">Parameters</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><code>items</code> - Array of carousel items (required)</li>
    <li><code>orientation</code> - <code>'horizontal'</code> (default) or <code>'vertical'</code></li>
    <li><code>autoplay</code> - Boolean to enable autoplay (default: <code>false</code>)</li>
    <li><code>autoplayDelay</code> - Delay between slides in milliseconds (default: <code>3000</code>)</li>
    <li><code>showNavigation</code> - Boolean to show navigation buttons (default: <code>true</code>)</li>
    <li><code>showIndicators</code> - Boolean to show indicators (default: <code>true</code>)</li>
    <li><code>ariaLabel</code> - ARIA label for the carousel (default: <code>'Carousel'</code>)</li>
    <li><code>class</code> - Additional CSS classes</li>
    <li><code>attrs</code> - Additional HTML attributes</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h3 id="events">Events</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <p>The carousel component dispatches the following custom events:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>basecoat:initialized</code> - Fired when the carousel is initialized</li>
    <li><code>basecoat:carousel:change</code> - Fired when the current slide changes
      <ul>
        <li><code>detail.currentIndex</code> - The index of the current slide</li>
        <li><code>detail.currentItem</code> - The current slide element</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h3 id="keyboard-navigation">Keyboard Navigation</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Arrow Left/Right</strong> - Navigate between slides (horizontal orientation)</li>
    <li><strong>Arrow Up/Down</strong> - Navigate between slides (vertical orientation)</li>
    <li><strong>Home</strong> - Go to first slide</li>
    <li><strong>End</strong> - Go to last slide</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h3 id="touch-support">Touch Support</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Swipe Left/Right</strong> - Navigate between slides (horizontal orientation)</li>
    <li><strong>Swipe Up/Down</strong> - Navigate between slides (vertical orientation)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h2 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h2>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li>Uses proper ARIA attributes for screen readers</li>
